General.Name: DORO AB
General.Description: Doro AB (publ), a technology company, develops telecom products and services for seniors. The company offers easy-to-use mobile and smart phones; home telephones; and accessories, including protective covers, wallet cases, and screen protectors. It also provides assistance key services. The company sells its products in approximately 27 countries. Doro AB (publ) was incorporated in 1972 and is headquartered in Malmö, Sweden.
